description:
Kaley Cuoco and her boyfriend Ryan Sweeting wrap their arms around each other while grabbing a bite to eat at Marmalade Cafe on Saturday (September 14) in Sherman Oaks, Calif.本周六（9月14日），Kaley Cuoco和她新男友Ryan Sweeting被看到在加利福尼亚大街上两人手挽手去果酱咖啡馆吃饭。

Later in the day, the 27-year-old actress and the 26-year-old tennis player were seen stocking up groceries at Whole Foods supermarket.当天晚些时候，27岁的Kaley和26岁的网球选手男友又被看到一起去Whole Foodstuff超市买东西。

Earlier in the week, Kaley was spotted enjoying a cup of coffee.本周早些时候，Kaley也被记者看到正在享受一杯美味咖啡。

“Come see my gorgeous sista @bricuoco sing some sweet songs this Monday night at bar Lubitch 9pm,” Kaley recently tweeted.Kaley最近还发了Twitter说“大家周一晚9点来Lubitch酒吧来看我的好姐妹@bricuoco唱歌吧。”
